#            **Canvas P2P web-application framework** — a TypeScript /
#            Node.js framework for building peer-to-peer
#            decentralized applications where the entire application
#            state (typed user accounts + actions + database
#            mutations) is persisted as a typed signed action log
#            ("GossipLog") that propagates over libp2p between
#            users' devices.  Every action is signed by the user's
#            typed cryptographic identity (Ethereum / Cosmos /
#            Solana / Substrate / AT Protocol / SIWE — Sign-In With
#            Ethereum), every database row is the typed
#            deterministic projection of the action log, and the
