#            centralized server (a single `canvas run` process
#            backed by a typed local SQLite + typed Express HTTP
#            API + typed network-explorer UI) OR a typed peer-to-
#            peer mesh (multiple Canvas peers gossip-replicating
#            the same GossipLog via libp2p).  Used to build:  typed
#            forum-style social apps, typed game leaderboards, typed
#            polls + governance UIs, typed signed-message channels
#            (Farcaster-adjacent), and typed local-first
#            collaborative tools.  Canvas xyz is a venture-backed
